<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الْبَقَرَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٩ص١٥٤:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{ذَلِكَ الْكِتَابُ لَا رَيْبَ فِيهِ هُدًى لِلْمُتَّقِينَ}</span> <span class="c4">[البقرة: ٢]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مَعْمَرٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{ذَلِكَ الكِتَابُ}</span> <span class="c4">[البقرة: ٢]</span> <span class="c2">«هَذَا القُرْآنُ»</span> ,<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{لاَ رَيْبَ}</span> <span class="c4">[البقرة: ٢]</span>: <span class="c2">«لاَ شَكَّ»</span>،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{هُدًى لِلْمُتَّقِينَ}</span> <span class="c4">[البقرة: ٢]</span>: <span class="c2">«بَيَانٌ وَدِلاَلَةٌ»</span>،<span class="c5"> كَقَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{ذَلِكُمْ حُكْمُ اللَّهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[الممتحنة: ١٠]</span>: <span class="c2">«هَذَا حُكْمُ اللَّهِ»</span> ,<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>